				}
			]
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "The Beginning of a Lineage"
			tasks: [{
				id: "10000000000000C5"
				title: "Obtain a Cobblemon egg through breeding"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			title: "&bFirst Egg"
			x: 0.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["10000000000000C8"]
			description: [
				"Eggs hatch by accumulating steps — walk, ride, or travel enough distance and the egg will hatch."
				""
				"The fastest way to hatch is to have a Cobblemon with the &eFlame Body&r ability in your party. It halves the required steps, turning a long walk into a short one."
				""
				"The hatchling starts from level 1 with whatever IVs, nature, and moves it inherited. Your first hatchling won't be perfect — that's what the rest of this chapter is for."
				""
				"&7Tip: A Cobblemon with Flame Body in your party halves egg hatch steps.&r"
			]
			id: "10000000000000CC"
			min_width: 320
			rewards: [
				{
					count: 3
					id: "10000000000000CA"
					item: "cobblemon:rare_candy"
					type: "item"
				}
				{
					id: "10000000000000CB"
					item: "cobblemon:destiny_knot"
					type: "item"
				}
			]
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "New Life"
			tasks: [{
				id: "10000000000000C9"
				title: "Hatch a Cobblemon egg"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			title: "&bHatchling"
			x: 2.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["10000000000000CC"]
			description: [
				"A Cobblemon's &eNature&r affects its stat growth — each Nature boosts one stat and reduces another. For competitive breeding, you want a specific Nature that benefits your intended role."
				""
				"Give the parent with your desired Nature an &eEverstone&r to hold. The offspring will inherit that Nature guaranteed."
				""
				"This is the first piece of intentional breeding. Rather than hatching random Cobblemon and hoping for good results, you're now controlling the outcome."
				""
				"&7Tip: The offspring will always inherit the nature of the Everstone-holding parent.&r"
			]
			id: "10000000000000CF"
			min_width: 330
			rewards: [{
				id: "10000000000000CE"
				item: "cobblemon:everstone"
				type: "item"
			}]
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "Controlled Inheritance"
			tasks: [{
				id: "10000000000000CD"
				title: "Breed for a specific nature using an Everstone"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			title: "&bNature Seeker"
			x: 4.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["10000000000000CF"]
			description: [
				"&eIVs (Individual Values)&r are hidden stats that determine a Cobblemon's maximum potential. Each stat has an IV from 0 to 31 — a perfect IV of 31 means maximum growth in that stat."
				""
				"The &eDestiny Knot&r passes 5 of the parents' IVs to the offspring. Pair it with &ePower Items&r to target specific stats."
				""
				"Breeding for 4+ perfect IVs takes multiple generations of careful pairing. Start with the stats that matter most for your Cobblemon's role."
				""
				"&7Tip: Destiny Knot passes 5 IVs from parents — stack with Power Items for targeted stat breeding.&r"
			]
			id: "10000000000000D2"
			min_width: 340
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
				id: "2B4393446A5A31E0"
				item: "cobblemon:cheri_berry"
				random_bonus: 1
				type: "item"
			}]
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "Statistical Perfection"
			tasks: [{
