			description: [
				"The perfect partner: the right Nature, six perfect IVs, and a key egg move. This is the pinnacle of the breeding system."
				""
				"It takes patience. Multiple breeding generations, careful IV tracking, and a clear picture of what you want before you start. Use &eJust Enough Breeding (JEBr)&r to look up compatible breeding pairs and egg move chains — it removes the guesswork."
				""
				"When you hatch it, you'll know it was worth every step."
				""
				"&7Tip: Use JEBr to look up compatible breeding pairs and egg move chains efficiently.&r"
